Metadata-Version: 1.2
Name: depinfo
Version: 1.3.0
Summary: List a package's direct dependencies and their versions.
Home-page: https://github.com/Midnighter/dependency-info
Author: Moritz E. Beber
Author-email: midnighter@posteo.net
